    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Semi-schematic line drawings of Aculus gebeliae n. sp., female: L. Lateral view; AD. Prodorsal shield; em. Empodium; CG. Coxigenital region; IG. Internal genitalia. Scale bar = 50 Μm for L, AD and CG; 25 Μm for IG; 9 Μm for em." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267773/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267774>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Micrographs of Aculus gebeliae n. sp., female, as viewed under phase contrast: 1. Lateral view; 2. Ventral view; 3. Dorsal view. Scale bar = 20 Μm for 1 and 3; 10 Μm for 2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267774/files/figure.png" ;
